  "text": "Similar approaches were also used to model tropical cyclone (hurricane) occurrences. [CITATION_1] discuss various ways of defining the spatial grid for the aggregation. Various studies of tornado occurrence both in the UK [CITATION_2] and the USA [CITATION_3] have also used aggregated counts over fairly arbitrary spatio-temporal units. Furthermore, [CITATION_4] impose a spatial grid to capture the relationship between hail occurrence and large-scale meteorological variables.",
